message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MED, cs.AI, cs.NEURON - The paper involves the use of conditional generative adversarial networks for generating synthetic CT images for MR-only planning in head and neck cases. This involves image processing, machine learning, and medical applications, which are all relevant to computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), medical imaging (cs.MED), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NEURON).
